sources.description:
Scientists and military operatives races against time to decode a mysterious signal from deep space, only to find themselves face-to-face with a formidable alien presence. A captain wants to revive aliens in suspended animation, leading his lieutenant to lead a mutiny against him, as chaos erupts and the stakes skyrocket; they must unravel the secrets of this extraterrestrial threat before humanity faces catastrophic consequences in a heart-pounding battle for survival.

Original title: First Encounter (1997)  Alternative title: Moral Code

Director & Writer: Redge Mahaffey
Stars: Veronica Bird, Holly Fields, Trevor Goddard, Roddy Piper, Stacie Randall
Genre: Aliens, Sci-Fi Movie
